            "ratingValue": "3",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It was a good school with quality teaching, though the management always kept a distance from the parents of the students. My three children studied this school many years ago.\n\nIt is known that the standard of study is now very low and only cash is accepted for all payments except fees. Many good teachers left the school probably because they were not paid well.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Campion School - Edapally"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Siyansh N"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-09-20",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I came here to write my CBSE Board Examinations in the year 2023.\nIt was the worst exam center of a school. Our school buses were asked to be parked outside, so we students had to walk to the school under the scorching sun. While we were writing examination, our beloved subject teachers who accompanied us were asked to wait under the tree by the playground. After some argument, they were made to wait in a warehouse sort of a room. Totally bizarre experience, according to my teachers. During one of my subject examinations, when I was trying to find my exam classroom, I sought for help from one of the teachers nearby, who refused to help me, telling me to find the classroom on my own. Like, are you for real? The very same day, when the answer booklets were being distributed, I found that on my answer booklet, the seal was already broken. We had written several complaints to CBSE regarding the issues we faced, and fortunately enough they were answered.\nI have friends who studied at this \"school\", and who agree with me. If you want a bright future for your child, there are MANY good schools out there, anything better than this place. Frankly enough, this doesn't even deserve half a star.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
